  "dialogue": {
    "19": {
      "id": "19",
      "speaker": "Halsin",
      "text": "For a while, after the shadow curse was lifted, I felt hope in a way that I hadn't felt in years.",
      "context": "NodeContext: Somewhat troubled by what he's seen of late. Part of a mini-arc where he dreams of a better world for all.",
      "checkflags": [
        "CURRENTREGION_BGO_Main_A",
        "ORI_Halsin_State_HeardDreamWYR = False",
        "ORI_Halsin_IPRD_WyrmsCrossingDream"
      ],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "16",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "12": {
          "id": "12",
          "speaker": "Halsin",
          "text": "I thought that nature would heal, and balance between it and civilisation could be restored, once and for all...",
          "context": "NodeContext: Somewhat troubled by what he's seen of late. Part of a mini-arc where he dreams of a better world for all.",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "16",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "25": {
              "id": "25",
              "speaker": "Halsin",
              "text": "Yet since we neared the city, I have seen more and more signs that I was being naive. Refugees, orphans, the downtrodden... all being left behind.",
              "context": "NodeContext: Somewhat troubled by what he's seen of late. Part of a mini-arc where he dreams of a better world for all.",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "16",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "5": {
                  "id": "5",
                  "speaker": "Halsin",
                  "text": "Perhaps the Shadow Druids were right, in their own twisted way. If such sorrows are the fruits of civilisation, perhaps there can be no true balance between it and nature.",
                  "context": "NodeContext: Somewhat troubled by what he's seen of late. Part of a mini-arc where he dreams of a better world for all.",
                  "checkflags": [
                    "DEN_ShadowDruid_Event_StartDenouncingScene"
                  ],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "16",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "23": {
                      "id": "23",
                      "speaker": "Player",
                      "text": "What do you mean?",
                      "context": "NodeContext: Somewhat troubled by what he's seen of late. Part of a mini-arc where he dreams of a better world for all.",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "16",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "21": {
                          "id": "21",
                          "speaker": "Halsin",
                          "text": "Look around us - you will not have to search for long to see exactly what I mean.",
                          "context": "NodeContext: Somewhat troubled by what he's seen of late. Part of a mini-arc where he dreams of a better world for all.",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "16",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "13": {
                              "id": "13",
                              "speaker": "Halsin",
                              "text": "That poor girl, Yenna. This city will devour her as sure as any wild predator would do. Be it through malice or just neglect... her fate will be sealed by this place.",
                              "context": "NodeContext: Referring to an orphan girl the player encountered",
                              "checkflags": [
                                "WYR_MeetingYenna_State_EndedIntro",
                                "LOW_BhaalTemple_State_OrinLaezelKillsYenna = False",
                                "LOW_BhaalTemple_State_WasAbductedYenna = False"
                              ],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "16",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {}
                            },
                            "6": {
                              "id": "6",
                              "speaker": "Halsin",
                              "text": "Someone is planting bombs in children's toys - what madness is taking root in this place?",
                              "context": "NodeContext: referring to some boobytrapped toys the player found",
                              "checkflags": [
                                "WYR_MerchantsHouse_Knows_SecretInBasement"
                              ],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "9",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "16": {
                                  "id": "16",
                                  "speaker": "",
                                  "text": "",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
